From: vISA downstream patchset
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] component: expose complete non-executing preflight
Upstream-base: 3de16a61796ce02d29795e4a074f37a33e6ebd87
License: Apache-2.0

Expose CheckInstantiation on the public Component alias. It applies the same
required-import, kind, and parser-level subtype validation as Instantiate,
without executing the instantiation plan or a core start function. Instantiate
reuses the same helper, so preflight and live construction cannot drift. Tests
cover a matching host interface, missing and mismatched imports, and a trapping
core start that remains untouched until real instantiation.

